@track R4_KICK_DOCKER_SLOT_PICK_FIX
@state completed
@date 2026-04-27
@chain ←r4_hexa_real_parity_drift_lock_2026_04_27.convergence (Sub-V) ←r4_noise_envelope_module_extraction_2026_04_27.convergence (Sub-U)
@scope sub-X — root-cause fix for false-positive `all-claude-slots-exhausted` verdict emitted by kick_dispatch when the resolver lands the kick inside the hexa-runner docker container (mac_safe_landing per raw 44).  Bug surfaced while attempting to fire ω-cycle on the noise envelope module (post-Sub-U).
@principle 근본해결 + 증상 vs 원인 분리 + container-env 결정 surface 명시화

# 문제 진단
@symptom `nexus kick "noise envelope module ..."` returned `__KICK_RESULT__ FAIL ... reason=all-claude-slots-exhausted` even though `hexa run ~/core/hive/tool/claude_slot_pick.hexa --pick` directly returned slot 1 successfully.
@host_path Mac local resolver routed to docker (`route=docker reason=mac_safe_landing image=hexa-runner:latest caps=cpus=4,mem=4g`).
@root_cause _slot_pick_invocation_prefix() in tool/kick_dispatch.hexa preferred `$HOME/.hx/bin/hive-exec claude_slot_pick` whenever `_file_exists($HOME/.hx/bin/hive-exec)` was true. Inside the hexa-runner container, $HOME is bind-mounted from the host, so the symlink IS visible AND its target is reachable — but `hive-exec` is a node/bash script whose runtime deps (node, bash) are NOT installed in the minimal hexa-runner image. The exec failed with "command not found" → empty stdout → `_claude_pick_slot()` returned "" → kick interpreted as exhausted pool.
@evidence_a `docker run --rm -v "$HOME:$HOME" -e HOME=$HOME hexa-runner:latest run ~/core/hive/tool/claude_slot_pick.hexa --pick` → returns slot path correctly (proves direct hexa-run works inside container).
@evidence_b `docker run --rm --entrypoint bash hexa-runner:latest -c 'echo'` → "exec: bash: executable file not found in $PATH" (proves bash absent → hive-exec deps missing).
@evidence_c container entrypoint inspection: `[/usr/bin/tini -- /usr/local/bin/hexa] [help]` — entrypoint is hexa itself; no shell / node available for hive-exec invocation.

# 결정 path 평가
@path_a_install_node_in_image SKIP — adds ~30MB to hexa-runner, breaks raw 9 hexa-only-strict spirit (container should be pure hexa runtime), violates "minimal image" property that motivated raw 44 mac_safe_landing.
@path_b_remove_hive_exec_branch SKIP — hive-exec preference exists for a reason on host Mac (reuses raw 99 canonical CLI surface). Removing hurts all non-container callers.
@path_c_container_aware_branch CHOSEN — detect container env (/.dockerenv OR HEXA_RESOLVER_IN_CONTAINER=1, matching ~/.hx/bin/hexa resolver convention) AND skip hive-exec branch only inside container, falling back to direct hexa-run on $HOME/.hx/packages/nexus/cli/run.hexa pattern. Preserves both surfaces.
@path_d_runtime_executable_probe SKIP — could `exec hive-exec --version 2>/dev/null` to test executability, but adds latency to every slot pick + still has false-positive risk if hive-exec returns 0 on partial deps.

# 시행
@file tool/kick_dispatch.hexa (uchg unlock-edit-relock)
@diff _slot_pick_invocation_prefix(): added `let in_container = _file_exists("/.dockerenv") || env("HEXA_RESOLVER_IN_CONTAINER") == "1"` — branch on `!in_container && _file_exists(hive_exec)` instead of `_file_exists(hive_exec)` alone. Comments updated with Sub-X (2026-04-27) explanation citing the bind-mount + missing-deps root cause.
@chflags_lock kick_dispatch.hexa relocked uchg post-edit. .raw-audit row appended (raw 85 escalation-audit-trail).

# 검증
@verification_smoke_static `grep -A6 'fn _slot_pick_invocation_prefix' tool/kick_dispatch.hexa` 가 in_container 가드 포함 확인.
@verification_runtime kick 재발사 (HEXA_LOCAL=1 HEXA_RESOLVER_NO_REROUTE=1) 가 docker landing 자체를 우회하므로 본 분기는 우회되지만, 후속 docker-landed kick 에서 자동 적용. ω-cycle witness 생성 진행 중 (47KB+ 작성됨, B1-B5 + G1-G3+ enumerated).

# follow-up
@followup_kick_in_docker_e2e 다음 kick 이 자연스럽게 docker landing 경로 (resolver default) 로 발사될 때 `__KICK_RESULT__ PASS` 가 나와야 검증 완결. 별도 smoke kick 으로 직접 호출 (HEXA_RESOLVER_NO_REROUTE 없이) 가능.
@followup_subagent_dispatch_parity tool/subagent_dispatch.hexa 등 다른 hive-exec 호출 사이트가 있다면 동일 container-aware 가드 적용 필요. 본 cycle 은 _slot_pick_invocation_prefix 1 site 수정.
@followup_sub_w_cross_host_stale_oauth ubu1/ubu2 의 ~/.claude-claude*/ slot 디렉토리에 stale OAuth 토큰 (Apr 20 .claude.json) → kick 이 거기 dispatch 되면 401 invalid x-api-key. 별도 Sub-W 로 401 detection + auth-stale slot rotation OR cross-host slot pool sync 결정.

@verdict Sub-X landed — kick_dispatch.hexa container-aware slot-pick 가드 추가, raw 85 audit + chflags lock. docker landing path 의 false-positive `all-claude-slots-exhausted` 차단. noise-envelope-module ω-cycle 은 본 fix 와 별개로 Mac local bypass 경로로 진행 중.
